---
title: How can I update my sprites' offsets?
seoDescription: How to adjust Pokémon position on the menu screen
publishDate: '2022-09-03 14:40:00'
order: 0
---

First of all, make sure that all non flying Pokémon do have their feet on the bottom of the sprites. This will ensure greater shadow in Battle.

Once done: Open `cmd.bat` in your project's root and write `psdk --util=calc_front_offset_y` then `Enter`.

This should make sure all Pokémon are centered in menus!

